
Changelog v0.2.1
=================


Features
--------
- Vehicle ↔ Driver assignment
- Current driver endpoint
- Vehicle assignment history
- Assignment management UI
- Assignment page
- Driver selection modal
- JWT secured assignment API

Improvements
------------
- Vehicle table navigation to assignment page
- Vehicle header displayed in assignment page
- Better handling of assignment history
- Fixed authentication issues on assignment endpoints

Backend
-------
- New Assignment routes
- Multi-tenant assignment support
- Assignment history tracking

Frontend
--------
- AssignmentsPage
- AssignmentService
- Navigation from Vehicles